Package: prodigenr
Title: Project directory generator
Version: 0.1.9000
Authors@R: "Luke W. Johnston <lwjohnst@gmail.com> [aut, cre]"
Description: 
             Create a project or files from templates.  This allows
             projects to be quickly and easily created, as well as for
             them to be standardized.

Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
License: MIT
LazyData: true
Imports: rmarkdown,
    yaml,
    captioner,
    git2r
Suggests: pander,
    ggplot2,
    tidyr,
    dplyr
